      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [275ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>cracked black pepper</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>,<strong> rice vinegar </strong>and a very generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>– this is your <strong>turmeric stock</strong></p>",
