      "instruction": "<p>Wash, then add the<strong> spinach</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water </strong>all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach </strong>under <strong>cold running water </strong>until it’s cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze as much water out of the spinach as you can</p>",
